    <item>
      <title>法国避免极右翼获胜但马克龙无人执政</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/france-dodges-far-right-win-but-macron-has-no-one-who-can-govern</link>
      <description><![CDATA[玛丽娜·勒庞 (Marine Le Pen) 领导的极右翼政党在周日的选举中惨败，导致法国议会出现分裂，没有明显多数，法国正陷入长期的政治僵局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/france-dodges-far-right-win-but-macron-has-no-one-who-can-govern</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 05:55:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国撤回吊销罢工医生执照的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-08/urgent-south-korea-to-withdraw-plan-to-suspend-licenses-of-striking-doctors-to-resolve-medical-impasse</link>
      <description><![CDATA[首尔，韩国（美联社）——韩国周一表示，将撤回早先暂停罢工医生执照的计划，这是解决该国长达数月的医疗僵局的努力之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-08/urgent-south-korea-to-withdraw-plan-to-suspend-licenses-of-striking-doctors-to-resolve-medical-impasse</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 05:28:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平与奥尔班会谈时重申呼吁乌克兰停火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/hungary-s-orban-visits-china-fresh-off-meeting-with-putin</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国家主席习近平在与到访的匈牙利总理维克托·奥尔班的意外会晤中再次呼吁乌克兰停火，奥尔班自封的“和平使命”惹恼了欧洲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/hungary-s-orban-visits-china-fresh-off-meeting-with-putin</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 00:10:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国工党总理里夫斯将在首次演讲中公布工党的增长计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/uk-s-reeves-to-unveil-labour-s-growth-plan-in-first-major-speech</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 将于周一在担任财政大臣后的首次重要演讲中阐述新工党政府刺激私人投资的计划，该党试图借助上周在英国大选中的压倒性胜利来推动经济增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/uk-s-reeves-to-unveil-labour-s-growth-plan-in-first-major-speech</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
